[Unknown]: Please welcome your host, Amit Verma.

00:01:53.800 --> 00:01:55.000
[Amit Varma]: Welcome to The Seen and The Unseen.

00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:59.240
[Amit Varma]: My guest today is Snehal Pradhan, who has been a fast bowler for the Indian team,

00:01:59.440 --> 00:02:04.600
[Amit Varma]: a cricket journalist, a TV commentator, a radio commentator in multiple languages,

00:02:04.800 --> 00:02:11.000
[Amit Varma]: a YouTuber and someone who teaches both how to play cricket and how to do multimedia sports journalism.

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:13.600
[Amit Varma]: She may do many things, but she's not a dabbler.

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:15.920
[Amit Varma]: She's one of the best cricket writers in the game today.

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:17.240
[Amit Varma]: And in fact, a true all-rounder.

00:02:17.440 --> 00:02:19.400
[Amit Varma]: Her reportage can be vivid and evocative.

