[Amit Varma]: Her understanding of cricket, her mastery of the craft of writing,

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:35.200
[Amit Varma]: and most of all, her work ethic and willingness to learn new forms like YouTubing is crazy.

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:39.840
[Amit Varma]: I'm a Snehal Pradhan fanboy and was delighted when she agreed to come on the show.

